So all PowerSupplies have the same Efficiency? I guess that is what we had before..
https://github.com/openbmc/bmcweb/blob/40e4f380d645c6bbe6bd8050e501203798a0c488/redfish-core/lib/sensors.hpp#L2189
Yes, all PowerSupplies have the same efficiency. That is how it was implemented previously, and we can consider changing this in the future.

I still find this odd/unexpected. 
I guess when the PDI model was created, it was assumed all your PowerSupplies had the same Efficiency Rating? Can you alteast call this out in the commit msg..
